Megatron turned around, "Tell them to wait.." He said, then he thought.
"Actually, tell them to hunt down the enemies in this base that arent
supposed to be here" Megatron got the computer to punch up him a profile
of Slaughter and Quatro. He then downloaded it into Cyclonus. "Help them
out. Show them the pain you receive when you mess with us" he said
cruely.
